There are boards a plenty these days for connecting your custom hardware to the
Internet. When it comes to development however, like many things, some are
better tools for certain jobs than others. Every day this week I will post some
details around boards that I have used, along with code on how to accomplish the
same task for each. Today's IoT-enabler will be the Electric Imp
[http://electricimp.com/].


