uses an innovative "BlinkUp" process to accomplish this task. There are two
parts to this system. First there is a phototransistor on the Imp. Second is an
application for your phone that produces precisely time flashes of light. This
effectively establishes a means of communication to the Imp, allowing you to set
the SSID of your network.

